313
00:23:08,310 --> 00:23:08,880
That formation

314
00:23:09,240 --> 00:23:10,640
is called "Exchanging",

315
00:23:11,150 --> 00:23:11,880
and its purpose

316
00:23:12,190 --> 00:23:13,520
is merely to transfer
someone from one place

317
00:23:13,520 --> 00:23:14,310
to another place

318
00:23:14,310 --> 00:23:15,910
where the same formation is drawn.

319
00:23:16,190 --> 00:23:17,240
The purpose of this mirror

320
00:23:17,240 --> 00:23:19,520
is only to show where she is.

321
00:23:19,960 --> 00:23:22,070
That woman who looks exactly like you

322
00:23:22,600 --> 00:23:24,360
must have used
the same words to deceive her

323
00:23:24,640 --> 00:23:25,960
to confuse her mind.

324
00:23:39,240 --> 00:23:39,910
Miss Zhu.

325
00:23:46,960 --> 00:23:48,070
As expected,

326
00:23:48,960 --> 00:23:50,390
as long as I take on this face,

327
00:23:50,720 --> 00:23:52,480
you can do nothing with me.

328
00:23:54,190 --> 00:23:55,390
What a pity.

329
00:23:56,070 --> 00:23:57,600
You're actually so devoted

330
