and storms raged.

389
00:27:09,960 --> 00:27:13,720
The mountain gods and lake spirits
took human form to ask for the wine.

390
00:27:15,000 --> 00:27:16,790
That guy was so bold

391
00:27:17,240 --> 00:27:19,000
to let them drink it.

392
00:27:19,790 --> 00:27:22,150
Even immortals
collapsed drunk at his doorstep,

393
00:27:22,670 --> 00:27:24,670
revealing their true forms.

394
00:27:25,190 --> 00:27:28,880
It was a major embarrassment.

395
00:27:30,480 --> 00:27:31,240
What a pity.

396
00:27:32,310 --> 00:27:33,910
At that time,
I was on Penglai Fairy Island

397
00:27:34,000 --> 00:27:35,270
and didn't make it in time.

398
00:27:35,550 --> 00:27:36,640
I didn't get a single taste.

399
00:27:36,880 --> 00:27:38,030
But today,

400
00:27:38,430 --> 00:27:39,840
I've seen it here with you.

401
00:27:40,550 --> 00:27:41,760
I must thank you

402
00:27:42,030 --> 00:27:43,390
for fulfilling one of my wishes.

403
00:27:44,720 --> 00:27:47,550
This wine has been poisoned.

404
00:27:48,360 --> 00:27:50,880
If she drinks it, she'll surely die.

405
00:27:55,150 --> 00:27:56,430
I covered my eyes,

406
00:27:56,790 --> 00:27:58,430
and placed a deadly poison

407
00:27:58,430 --> 00:28:00,880
in one of the jars of wine.

408
00:28:01,670 --> 00:28:03,240
The poison is colorless and tasteless.

409
00:28:03,910 --> 00:28:07,520
Even you may not be able to tell.

410
00:28:09,720 --> 00:28:10,390
Indeed,

411
00:28:10,880 --> 00:28:12,880
this fine wine does not come easily.

412
00:28:13,390 --> 00:28:15,520
But the poison you used

413
00:28:15,910 --> 00:28:17,120
may not work on me.

414
00:28:17,360 --> 00:28:19,670
I don't want you to die.

415
00:28:20,430 --> 00:28:23,600
I just want you to sleep
for a thousand years.

416
00:28:24,430 --> 00:28:25,840
Do you remember

417
00:28:26,190 --> 00:28:27,360
the last time you came,

418
00:28:27,760 --> 00:28:30,190
you devoured eight million
of my Yangcheng citizens?

419
00:28:30,720 --> 00:28:32,310
Thousands of my kin

420
00:28:32,840 --> 00:28:35,030
were stuffed into wine jars by you.

421
00:28:37,960 --> 00:28:39,880
Now that you mention it, I remember.

422
00:28:39,880 --> 00:28:42,760
I did make drunken shrimp back then.

423
00:28:43,070 --> 00:28:44,190
Those I didn't finish

424
00:28:44,190 --> 00:28:45,910
were put back into the lake.

425
00:28:46,360 --> 00:28:47,960
No wonder you look drunk.

426
00:28:48,240 --> 00:28:49,310
Which one are you?

427
00:28:49,310 --> 00:28:50,550
Why are you still drunk now?

428
00:28:51,360 --> 00:28:52,390
Does it matter?

429
00:28:53,430 --> 00:28:56,430
I am just a nameless man.

430
00:28:57,030 --> 00:28:58,190
You don't need to worry

431
00:28:58,190 --> 00:28:59,600
I'll do anything to you today.

432
00:29:00,030 --> 00:29:01,240
At your age,

433
00:29:01,480 --> 00:29:02,360
even if you were made into wine,

434
00:29:02,640 --> 00:29:04,240
it would taste sour and unpleasant.

435
00:29:04,670 --> 00:29:05,640
Today I am here

436
00:29:06,070 --> 00:29:07,720
only to eat your master.

437
00:29:11,640 --> 00:29:13,360
I'm not sitting here

438
00:29:13,480 --> 00:29:15,360
for himself.

439
00:29:15,760 --> 00:29:17,480
I've waited a hundred years

440
00:29:17,670 --> 00:29:19,150
and have already grown old.

441
00:29:19,760 --> 00:29:21,360
Finally, heaven has eyes,

442
00:29:21,880 --> 00:29:24,310
letting me wait until today
for your arrival.

443
00:29:24,880 --> 00:29:26,720
Let's each take

444
00:29:26,720 --> 00:29:28,240
one jar of this wine,

445
00:29:28,240 --> 00:29:30,150
how about it?

446
00:29:31,310 --> 00:29:32,880
As long as I can stop you,

447
00:29:33,230 --> 00:29:36,110
it's worth all my efforts.

448
00:29:36,920 --> 00:29:38,040
You don't need to do this.

449
00:29:38,800 --> 00:29:40,560
I won't spare your master.

450
00:29:40,920 --> 00:29:42,040
As for this wine,

451
00:29:42,400 --> 00:29:44,110
I'll come back to drink it
after eating your master.

452
00:29:44,760 --> 00:29:46,880
I heard you came this time

453
00:29:46,880 --> 00:29:48,430
with a human companion.

454
00:29:48,950 --> 00:29:50,000
So what if I did?

455
00:29:50,160 --> 00:29:51,470
May I ask,

456
00:29:51,710 --> 00:29:53,230
how long does a human live?

457
00:29:53,920 --> 00:29:55,680
General, you roam this world

458
00:29:55,760 --> 00:29:57,190
for how many years

459
00:29:57,230 --> 00:30:00,230
and how many people
have crossed paths with you?

460
00:30:01,230 --> 00:30:03,470
Drinking, singing,
and living in splendor.

461
00:30:03,560 --> 00:30:05,880
Where are they now?

462
00:30:05,880 --> 00:30:06,950
Where is Duan Qingtang?

463
00:30:07,760 --> 00:30:09,040
Where is Mei Dongjing?

464
00:30:09,760 --> 00:30:11,400
Where's Monk Lotus,

465
00:30:11,400 --> 00:30:13,470
who gave you your name

466
00:30:13,470 --> 00:30:14,920
and trapped you in Wuxia City?

467
00:30:15,920 --> 00:30:18,590
In the end,
you are the only one left here.

468
00:30:19,230 --> 00:30:20,190
From now on,

469
00:30:20,350 --> 00:30:22,350
there will be endless years.

470
00:30:22,590 --> 00:30:23,590
The nights will be long,

471
00:30:23,760 --> 00:30:27,190
and you will remain alone.

472
00:31:06,040 --> 00:31:06,680
You're right.

473
00:31:08,110 --> 00:31:09,520
Where is he now?

474
00:31:12,710 --> 00:31:13,560
Who are you really?

475
00:31:14,110 --> 00:31:15,470
Why do you know so much?

476
00:31:15,710 --> 00:31:17,950
No need to worry.

477
00:31:18,560 --> 00:31:20,590
All things are transient

478
00:31:20,760 --> 00:31:21,920
like bubbles and shadows,

479
00:31:21,920 --> 00:31:23,070
dreams and illusions,

480
00:31:23,070 --> 00:31:24,710
dew and lightning.

481
00:31:25,350 --> 00:31:27,560
You've lived a thousand years

482
00:31:27,920 --> 00:31:29,350
but still can't comprehend

483
00:31:29,640 --> 00:31:31,470
and let go the obsession in your heart.

484
00:31:31,710 --> 00:31:33,000
You've repeated the mistake.

485
00:31:33,640 --> 00:31:35,190
So why cling to it?

486
00:31:36,110 --> 00:31:39,040
Why not seize the day
and enjoy the wine?

