00:33:20,640 --> 00:33:21,430
you're eloquent.

504
00:33:22,710 --> 00:33:24,710
Lord Wuchang is lucky to have

505
00:33:24,710 --> 00:33:25,680
such a loyal subordinate like you.

506
00:33:26,920 --> 00:33:27,880
But it's a pity

507
00:33:28,830 --> 00:33:29,680
that all of this

508
00:33:30,470 --> 00:33:31,640
