579
00:37:32,630 --> 00:37:34,150
You're just as coward

580
00:37:34,590 --> 00:37:35,800
as you used to be.

581
00:37:37,520 --> 00:37:38,430
Why don't you step aside?

582
00:37:40,350 --> 00:37:41,960
