00:37:45,960 --> 00:37:46,960
Now, I

585
00:37:47,870 --> 00:37:49,960
also have people behind me
I must protect,

586
00:37:50,910 --> 00:37:51,830
so I cannot retreat.

587
00:37:53,110 --> 00:37:54,320
My master has not yet escaped danger,

588
00:37:55,720 --> 00:37:56,870
so I dare not die either.

589
00:38:06,110 --> 00:38:06,760
Last time,

590
00:38:07,630 --> 00:38:10,280
I made brewed crab.

591
00:38:11,110 --> 00:38:11,870
And this time,

592
00:38:12,480 --> 00:38:14,280
I've invented a new recipe,

593
00:38:14,520 --> 00:38:15,670
hand-washed crab.

594
00:38:16,520 --> 00:38:19,830
First, chop your master into pieces,

595
00:38:20,150 --> 00:38:21,390
then fry with sesame oil.

596
00:38:22,190 --> 00:38:24,320
Finally, add ten seasonings,

597
00:38:24,560 --> 00:38:25,190
mix them well

598
00:38:25,560 --> 00:38:26,430
and it's ready to eat.

599
00:38:26,960 --> 00:38:27,520
How does that sound?

600
00:38:27,760 --> 00:38:28,870
As a servant,

601
00:38:30,080 --> 00:38:31,430
I shall be loyal and righteous

602
00:38:31,430 --> 00:38:32,390
and protect my master.

603
00:38:32,960 --> 00:38:34,320
But I'm not competent enough

604
00:38:35,080 --> 00:38:37,000
and suffered such
great pain and humiliation.

605
00:38:37,280 --> 00:38:39,320
I truly feel ashamed.

606
00:38:39,390 --> 00:38:41,110
Loyalty,

607
00:38:41,870 --> 00:38:43,760
righteousness.

608
00:38:47,760 --> 00:38:48,760
Who among you

609
00:38:49,960 --> 00:38:51,040
dares to say

610
00:38:51,040 --> 00:38:52,630
these words in front of me?

611
00:38:52,870 --> 00:38:53,480
General.

612
00:38:57,430 --> 00:38:59,110
Your always like
to bring up old matters.

613
00:39:00,430 --> 00:39:01,720
Hundreds of years have passed.

614
00:39:02,560 --> 00:39:04,720
Why do you still cling to them?

615
00:39:05,190 --> 00:39:06,350
Enough nonsense!

616
00:39:09,080 --> 00:39:09,670
Miss Zhu.

617
00:39:13,830 --> 00:39:14,720
If not now,

618
00:39:15,150 --> 00:39:16,000
when will you take action?

619
00:39:28,520 --> 00:39:29,240
Stop.

620
00:39:30,670 --> 00:39:31,720
Stop, all of you.

621
00:39:32,150 --> 00:39:32,960
Stop it, everyone.

622
00:39:33,910 --> 00:39:35,350
Do not be disrespectful to General.

623
00:39:36,190 --> 00:39:36,800
Master.

624
00:39:37,280 --> 00:39:38,110
Why have you come out?

625
00:39:38,110 --> 00:39:38,760
Insolent!

626
00:39:39,390 --> 00:39:40,630
Who permitted you to act like this?

627
00:39:41,480 --> 00:39:42,080
Fengyi,

628
00:39:42,480 --> 00:39:44,240
do you not know my principles?

629
00:39:48,150 --> 00:39:48,760
General.

630
00:39:49,280 --> 00:39:50,190
Wuchang,

631
00:39:50,960 --> 00:39:52,760
how dare you set layers of traps for me.

632
00:39:54,560 --> 00:39:56,150
Do you think I'll spare you lightly?

633
00:40:01,430 --> 00:40:02,240
I admit guilt.

634
00:40:04,830 --> 00:40:06,150
500 years ago,

635
00:40:07,110 --> 00:40:09,240
you faced a heavenly calamity
and great disaster,

636
00:40:09,560 --> 00:40:11,080
and were saved by Master Lotus.

637
00:40:11,280 --> 00:40:12,480
You made a vow

638
00:40:12,720 --> 00:40:14,720
to repay him with your life.

639
00:40:14,720 --> 00:40:16,630
Is this true or not?

640
00:40:16,720 --> 00:40:17,150
True.

641
00:40:17,480 --> 00:40:18,000
Then how did you

642
00:40:19,240 --> 00:40:20,480
repay him?

643
00:40:24,320 --> 00:40:25,560
It's fault.

644
00:40:26,480 --> 00:40:28,830
I've always felt
deeply ashamed towards you.

645
00:40:29,150 --> 00:40:31,240
Naturally, I should willingly
offer myself for you.

646
00:40:31,910 --> 00:40:33,080
Since it's your own choice,

647
00:40:34,480 --> 00:40:35,430
then what about now?

648
00:40:36,430 --> 00:40:39,390
You've schemed to take my life.

649
00:40:40,430 --> 00:40:41,590
You're not just

650
00:40:41,590 --> 00:40:43,280
a cowardly rat,

651
00:40:43,630 --> 00:40:44,350
but also

652
00:40:44,350 --> 00:40:46,000
a hypocrite cloaked in righteousness.

653
00:40:46,480 --> 00:40:47,000
General,

654
00:40:48,000 --> 00:40:49,320
I did not plot against you.

655
00:40:49,320 --> 00:40:50,390
Still pretending!

656
00:40:50,480 --> 00:40:50,960
General.

657
00:40:50,960 --> 00:40:51,350
I...

658
00:40:52,960 --> 00:40:54,110
Don't blame Master.

659
00:40:54,910 --> 00:40:56,110
It was I who did it.

660
00:41:29,990 --> 00:41:35,720
♪Here's a flower for you♪

661
00:41:36,380 --> 00:41:40,860
♪I don't know what to say
when we look at each other♪

662
00:41:42,710 --> 00:41:48,490
♪Time goes by so quickly♪

663
00:41:48,840 --> 00:41:54,170
♪My obsession leads to my fate♪

664
00:41:54,670 --> 00:42:00,500
♪Destiny is confusing over the years♪

665
00:42:01,090 --> 00:42:07,030
♪It feels bleak even with the light on♪

666
00:42:07,380 --> 00:42:10,570
♪I see the shadow
when I almost forget you♪

667
00:42:10,570 --> 00:42:13,930
♪A ray of light on my journey♪

668
00:42:13,930 --> 00:42:20,120
♪It's like you're here
to pour out your heart♪

669
00:42:20,240 --> 00:42:26,260
♪Although the memories of our love
bring us pain♪

670
00:42:26,680 --> 00:42:32,830
♪All I ask for is to hold your hand
until the end of time♪

671
00:42:32,990 --> 00:42:36,150
♪Selflessly♪

672
00:42:36,300 --> 00:42:39,700
♪We taste the sorrows and joys♪

673
00:42:40,180 --> 00:42:47,180
♪I'll never let you go
till death do us part♪
